      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AROUND OUTSIDE (1) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Shima Moon (17.94) in a Maiden. Has the pace to be prominent. Makes plenty of appeal. HIGH COBBER (8) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 1.75 lengths into second (17.84) at this track in a Maiden over 305m. Expected to be in the finish again. SWIFT GENO (7) will need a clean break from an outside box at his debut. Ratings suggest a place chance. HANNI ROCKS (2) is by Tommy Shelby out of Rock It Barcia making debut. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Can sneak into the frame at her first appearance.",
